{
  "stem": "8725.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, Helen, when I met her, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] she was telling me about he father that was killed by the Germans.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That he was not in any organization but they were partisans.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And if partisans did something to even the car of a German, then the German did go to their first homes and pull out men and shot them.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so she say she's alone with her mother and they are having very hard time.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They don't have money and this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I did have enough food from the office when I served so I shared it with them.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And soon Helen told me that she was engaged to a Jewish man, Henry Weinbaum.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that they were supposed to get married and now the Germans took him away.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She doesn't know where.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And she just tried to find if they're bringing new Jewish people from the neighborhoods.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You know, she tries to find it out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And one day she said to me, Irene, there is a new group coming.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I know somebody said that you know that Henry is dead.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So she asked me to go with her.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So I, and Jeanina, my sister, and her mother, we took a bus.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I told the Shultz, that I finded friends and that I would like to spend it with her some time.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we went to that-- not far from Lviv, from the center of the town.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "You know, we walked maybe three, four, five blocks.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And when we come there, there were many people there already.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "There were barbed wire fencing and barbed wire gate.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And of a second the SS step out and start shooting in the air.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And [GERMAN]!",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "You go out!",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And chasing everybody.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Chasing everybody.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
